---
// Value Proposition Section - Three Pillars
---

<section class="value-proposition">
  <div class="value-content">
    <h2>Built on Three Pillars</h2>
    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Empathy-Driven Innovation</h3>
        <p>We solve complex problems with elegant solutions that put the end-user first.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Quality by Design</h3>
        <p>Accessible software is inherently betterâ€”more robust, usable, and scalable.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Seamless Collaboration</h3>
        <p>Direct, frictionless communication ensuring your vision translates perfectly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .value-proposition {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 120px 20px;
    background: white;
  }

  .value-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .value-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.441em;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0 0 60px 0;
    color: rgb(var(--black));
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .pillar {
    background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
    padding: 40px 30px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .pillar:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .pillar-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .pillar-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .pillar h3 {
    font-size: 1.563em;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    color: rgb(var(--black));
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .pillar p {
    font-size: 1.1em;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Mobile responsive */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .value-proposition {
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .value-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.953em;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .pillars-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .pillar {
      padding: 30px 24px;
    }
  }

  /* Dark mode */
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .value-proposition {
      background: rgb(var(--black));
    }

    .value-content h2 {
      color: rgb(var(--gray-light));
    }

    .pillar {
      background: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
    }

    .pillar h3 {
      color: rgb(var(--gray-light));
    }

    .pillar p {
      color: rgb(var(--gray));
    }

    .pillar:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
  }
</style>
